    "sidepanelcontent": "[p][b]Related Profession[/b][br]\r\n@[Blacksmith](profession:550d5568-3a82-4eab-8f23-1e283bd79b19)[/p]\r\n[p][b]Related Titles and Ranks[/b][br]\r\n@[Weaponsmith](rank:7ae58d32-f66f-4515-8f9e-79652e890384)[br]\r\n@[Armoursmith](rank:c85f1b19-0bdb-4c9a-8f2c-8cc0c93e70ad)[br]\r\n@[Bladesmith](rank:beedc6ab-0db9-4904-a1c0-aac5bd59a2bb)[/p]",
