    "fullfooter": "[aloud]\r\n[container:row][container:col-md-6][h4]Schedule[/h4][/container][container:col-md-6][h4]Rules[/h4][/container][/container]\r\n[container:row][container:col-md-2]Entry Prep[/container][container:col-md-4]Morning[/container][container:col-md-6][center] - Materials used during the competition must be supplied by the Blacksmithing Academy. If you want to supply a special material, it must be approved by the board of the Academy before the start of the event.[/center][br][/container][/container]\r\n[container:row][container:col-md-2]Start Smithing[/container][container:col-md-4]Noon[/container][container:col-md-6][center] - Participants are expected to arrive a few hours before the smithing starts. They are expected to prepare their forge and inspect their gear beforehand.[br][b]Remember: This part is also judged![/b][/center][br][/container][/container]\r\n[container:row][container:col-md-2]End Smithing[/container][container:col-md-4]Mid Afternoon[/container][container:col-md-6][center] - Sabotaging other particpants and cheating result in direct disqualification of the event. Furthermore you'll be removed from the academy.[/center][br][/container][/container]\r\n[container:row][container:col-md-2]Judgement[/container][container:md-4]Late Afternoon[/container][/container]\r\n\r\n[center][h4]AUCTION AND FEAST UNTIL WE'RE ALL PASSED OUT[/h4][/center]\r\n[/aloud]",
    "authornotes": null,
    "scrapbook": "- Competition for student blacksmiths on who can create the best piece of work\r\n- It's the \"final exam\" of the blacksmithing academy\r\n- Students show off what they have learned and where their skillset lies\r\n- Master blacksmiths are present to judge the work of the students\r\n\t- They get to pick which student(s) they would like to have as an apprentice\r\n  - Master blacksmits from other cities also come to this event, as the blacksmithing academy is known to produce some of the finest apprentices\r\n\r\n- After the competition, the works of the students are auctioned off which gives them some money to get a start in life",
